        <td headers="Definition" bgcolor='#F2F2F2'>This is the destination VLAN/port to send the traffic to.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td headers="Term" scope="row" bgcolor='#E9E7E8'>RSPAN VLAN</td>
        <td headers="Definition" bgcolor='#E9E7E8'><textformat blockindent="-16"><ul><li>A unique VLAN is required to transport the traffic from one switch to another.</li><li>The VLAN is configured with the<font face="_typewriter"><b> remote-span </b></font>vlan configuration command.</li><li>This VLAN must be defined on all switches in the path and must also be allowed on trunk ports between the source and destination.</li></ul></textformat></td>
